data.description: If you are looking for a little piece of country heaven, you won't want to miss out on this home. Nestled between the corn fields yet you can still have pizza delivered all while watching those country sunsets? Unheard of! With over 2800 sqft 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths and completely updated. This home offers the space and the country chic style everyone is raving about. With a large detached heated barn with work station and plenty of room to store all the toys, you'll find yourself checking off all the boxes.  Updates since 2020: 3 stage water filtration system, Hot water heater, water pressure tank, HVAC system, new appliances, new flooring, new subflooring, new  drywall, freshly painted inside and outside, crown molding, light fixtures, kitchen cabinets, quartz counter tops, windows, dehumidifier, serviced drainage system, new 24x24 back patio, new doors throughout.
